title: The Walking Dead Season 6 Episodes 1-12
description:
S6, Ep1
11 Oct. 2015
First Time Again
Still reeling from the deaths of Reg and Pete, Rick and the group devise a plan to lure a massive herd of walkers away from Alexandria, but a new development puts the entire community at risk. 


S6, Ep2
18 Oct. 2015
JSS
Carol and Morgan lead a line of defense against The Wolves when Alexandria comes under attack. 


S6, Ep3
25 Oct. 2015
Thank You
In a race against time, Glenn and Michonne try to lead the Alexandrians back home before the herd catches up to them. 


S6, Ep4
1 Nov. 2015
Here's Not Here
Morgan tells the Wolves' leader about his journey from King County to Alexandria, where he met a lone survivor with a code. 


S6, Ep5
8 Nov. 2015
Now
Alexandria recovers from the Wolves' attack. Maggie and Aaron search for Glenn. Deanna questions her leadership. 


S6, Ep6
15 Nov. 2015
Always Accountable
Wounded after being separated from Abraham and Sasha, Daryl finds himself captive of three survivors on the run. 


S6, Ep7
22 Nov. 2015
Heads Up
Glenn and Enid make their way back to Alexandria. Meanwhile, the tension between Carol and Morgan rises. 


S6, Ep8
29 Nov. 2015
Start to Finish
With no way out, Rick and the people of Alexandria must defend the community against the invading herd. 

S6, Ep9
14 Feb. 2016
No Way Out
Daryl, Abraham and Sasha face-off against the Saviors. In Alexandria, Rick and his group make their way through the herd. 


S6, Ep10
21 Feb. 2016
The Next World
Rick and Daryl go on a run where they meet Jesus, a mysterious man with many secrets. Michonne follows Spencer as he tries to find his mother. Carl and Enid have a strange interaction in the woods. 


S6, Ep11
28 Feb. 2016
Knots Untie
Jesus takes Rick and the group to the Hilltop Colony, a peaceful community overshadowed by the power of Negan and The Saviors. 


S6, Ep12
6 Mar. 2016
Not Tomorrow Yet
As the joint forces of Alexandria and the Hilltop attack the Saviors' compound, Carol and Maggie fall into a trap
